Initialize a new Git repository in the "development" directory
    cd development && git init && git add . && git status

Reset the Git staging area
    git reset && git add . && git status

Add files and commit
    git add . 
    git commit -m "Initial commit: grbgtest with Google Drive integration and chat interface"

Add the remote repository:
    git remote add origin https://github.com/madhudv1/testgrbg.git

Push the code to GitHub
    git push -u origin main